title: Eva Longoria Returns!
itunes:title: Eva Longoria Returns!
itunes:subtitle: Eva Longoria [Desperate Housewives, Telenovela, Overboard] returns to Unqualified to catch up on everything that’s happened since she and Anna last saw each other. They talk about working together on Overboard, how Eva became a director, empowering women
description:
Eva Longoria [Desperate Housewives, Telenovela, Overboard] returns to Unqualified to catch up on everything that’s happened since she and Anna last saw each other. They talk about working together on Overboard, how Eva became a director, empowering women in the entertainment industry and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined once again by online dating expert Mark Brooks to answer questions and offer advice on how to approach the world of internet dating.
